 <h2>🍁 Pre-Winter</h2>
            <p><b>Months:</b> November - December</p>
            <p>
                Temperatures begin to fall. The climate becomes cool and
                pleasant before the arrival of winter.
            </p>
        </div>
<div class="season winter">  
